</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="B6DC9EABFFF0FFAAFC91712EDC22FA42" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE79CD20FFF0FFAAFC91712EDC22FA42" blockId="65.[794,1399,1033,1473]" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">
This recently described genus currently includes five species, the 
<typeStatus id="217D7382FFF0FFAAFC17710DDBB2FBC1" box="[924,970,1066,1090]" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">type</typeStatus>
species 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFBAE710DDD0BFBC2" authority="(CAMERON, 1939)" baseAuthorityName="CAMERON" baseAuthorityYear="1939" box="[1061,1395,1065,1089]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Tetrabothrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubricollis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFBAE710DDCD0FBC2" box="[1061,1192,1065,1089]" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">E. rubricollis</emphasis>
(CAMERON, 1939)
</taxonomicName>
, originally described from North 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF0FFAAFBF6716EDCCDFBE2" box="[1149,1205,1097,1121]" name="India" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">India</collectingCountry>
(CAMERON 1939) and subsequently reported also from South 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF0FFAAFB73714EDD48FB02" box="[1272,1328,1129,1153]" name="India" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">India</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF0FFAAFACB714EDB29FB22" author="PACE, R." pageId="65" pageNumber="78" pagination="31 - 47" refId="ref77870" refString="PACE, R. 2001: Aleocharinae nuove o poco note dell'India (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Nouvelle Revue d'Entomologie (N. S.) 18 (1): 31 - 47." type="journal article" year="2001">PACE 2001</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFCEF71ADDC35FB22" authority="(PACE, 1992)" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="1992" box="[868,1101,1161,1185]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Episkiodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="franzi">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFCEF71ADDBC5FB22" box="[868,957,1161,1185]" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">E. franzi</emphasis>
(PACE, 1992)
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF0FFAAFB1A71AEDCAAFB22" box="[1169,1234,1161,1185]" name="Nepal" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">Nepal</collectingCountry>
, 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFB5571ADDC78FB42" authority="(PACE, 2008)" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="2008" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Episkiodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="neocoenonicacollis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFB5571ADDB1CFB42" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">E. neocoenonicacollis</emphasis>
(PACE, 2008)
</taxonomicName>
from Borneo, 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFB3A718DDBE9FB62" authority="PACE, 2013" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Episkiodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malayrubricollis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFB3A718DDD0FFB42" box="[1201,1399,1193,1217]" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">E. malayrubricollis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF0FFAAFC9171EEDBE9FB62" author="PACE, R." box="[794,913,1225,1249]" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE, 2013</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from Peninsular 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF0FFAAFBDA71EEDCC9FB62" box="[1105,1201,1225,1249]" name="Malaysia" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFB6571EDDBE8FA82" authority="PACE, 2013" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2013" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Episkiodrusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="veluticollis">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFB6571EDDD0FFB62" box="[1262,1399,1225,1249]" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">E. veluticollis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF0FFAAFC9171CEDBE8FA82" author="PACE, R." box="[794,912,1257,1281]" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE, 2013</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="86D18DB0FFF0FFAAFC5871CEDC58FA82" box="[979,1056,1257,1281]" name="Taiwan" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF0FFAAFBBB71CEDCDDFA82" author="PACE, R." box="[1072,1189,1257,1281]" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE 2013</bibRefCitation>
). Based on external characters, particularly the morphology of the pronotum and the dense non-setiferous punctation on tergite VII, this species is unlikely to be closely allied to 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFAAA706EDD0EFAE2" authorityName="LEACH" authorityYear="1819" box="[1313,1398,1353,1377]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFAAA706EDD0EFAE2" box="[1313,1398,1353,1377]" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">Drusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as suggested by 
<bibRefCitation id="9A57B0D1FFF0FFAAFC58704EDC26FA02" author="PACE, R." box="[979,1118,1385,1409]" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" pagination="33 - 63" refId="ref78152" refString="PACE, R. 2013: New distributional data, new species and three new genera of Aleocharinae from Malaysia, Vietnam and Taiwan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Tropical Zoology 26 (1): 33 - 63." type="journal article" year="2013">PACE (2013)</bibRefCitation>
. According to CAMERON (1939), the sculpture of tergite VII resembles that of 
<taxonomicName id="39C6B6A3FFF0FFAAFAB470AEDC2EFA42" authority="CAMERON, 1939" authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pheidologitonetes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="65" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCB21132FFF0FFAAFAB470AEDBD9FA42" italics="true" pageId="65" pageNumber="78">Pheidologitonetes</emphasis>
CAMERON, 1939
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
